data.title: Ethereum’s End-Of-Year Rally Still At Play? Analysts Eye 50% December Jump
data.description: Ethereum (ETH) is attempting to bounce from the market’s Q4 correction, retesting the $3,000 barrier once again. As we approach the end of November, some market observers have suggested that the end-of-year rally may still be possible in the coming weeks.Ethereum Eyes $3,000 Ahead Of Key UpgradeOn…
